November BAWG Meeting Agenda Cc Attached please find a Word document for the November BAWG meeting agenda Also attached please find an Excel file with very rough first draft of a list of BAWG issues This file will be discussed under agenda item The goal will be to solicit comments from the BAWG members and NYISO Grid Accounting staff at the November meeting to correct all the rows and columns of this spreadsheet Eventually this will be the official disclosed list of BAWG issues posted on the NYISO web site per approved NYSEG motion from the November BIC meeting Wes Yeomans See attached file BAWGagendadoc See attached file bawgactionitemsxls BAWGagendadoc bawgactionitemsxls
